~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Updation during reflection~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
There are two candidate CDs. 
 The positive CD has the following information: The Wall: double‑album concept epic of side‑spanning suites, recurring motifs and continuous narrative; theatrical lead vocals, layered studio textures, evolving guitar solos and extended instrumentals; wide dramatic dynamics, immersive remastering, live/film extensions, exhaustive liner notes and deluxe packaging for listeners who prefer sustained, attentive listening.. 
